k\": 3.905874635325504e-05, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a stunning turn of events, Marcial bowed to Uzbekistan's Turabek Khabibullaev via unanimous decision in the round of 16 of the men's 80kg at the North Paris Arena on\\u00a0Tuesday, July 30 (Wednesday, July 31, Manila time).\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 497, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9989119294135362, \"rank\": 0.0010793456155965577, \"text\": \"Uzbekistan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 604, \"end\": 609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999966109954, \"rank\": 3.389035561334324e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 657, \"end\": 663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"score\": 0.9991977705300116, \"rank\": 0.0008024807009833913, \"text\": \"Manila\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the Philippines' top medal bets, Marcial - who wonbronzein the Tokyo Games - got the boot in his opening bout as Khabibullaev won with scores of 30-27, 29-28, 29-28, 29-28, 29-28.\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 683, \"end\": 694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9999607687856449, \"rank\": 3.905874635325504e-05, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\",